videos.headline: 81-yard TD dash for SDSU's Penny
videos.description: Aztecs RB Rashaad Penny finds the hole and breaks away for an 81-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (81-yard TD dash for SDSU's Penny) 2017/12/23

videos.headline: Black Knights' Bradshaw runs in TD
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw runs through the gap for Army's first touchdown.

videos.headline: Aztecs' Rosales ejected from game
videos.description: SDSU's G Antonio Rosales, playing for first time in six games, is called for two unsportsmanlike conduct penalties on one play and is ejected.

videos.headline: Penny finds crease for 2nd TD run
videos.description: Aztecs' Rashaad Penny squeezes through the defense and runs 32 yards for his second touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Army's Woolfolk pushes his way into end zone
videos.description: Darnell Woolfolk wrestles his way into the end zone for another Black Knights' touchdown.

videos.headline: SDSU's Washington runs back a 78-yard kickoff return TD
videos.description: Juwan Washington zig-zags down the field 78 yards, dodging multiple tackles, for a San Diego State kickoff return touchdown.

videos.headline: Black Knights' Davidson slips his way into end zone
videos.description: Army's Andy Davidson runs in for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Monken 'most embarrassed' about missing anthem
videos.description: Army head coach Jeff Monken apologizes for accidentally missing the national anthem and discusses the silly mistakes the team made in the first half.

videos.headline: Penny sprints 49 yards for another TD
videos.description: Rashaad Penny finds another gap in the defense and bolts 49 yards for his third touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: SDSU's Luke picks off Army's trick play
videos.description: Kjetil Cline is intercepted by San Diego State's Anthony Luke, who returns it for 21 yards.

videos.headline: Army intercepts pass off deflection
videos.description: San Diego State QB Christian Chapman gets picked off when the ball is deflected and is caught by Alex Aukerman who returns it 11 yards.

videos.headline: Black Knights' Bradshaw bursts loose for TD
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw cuts up the gut and runs 27 yards for a game-tying Army touchdown.

videos.headline: Penny bumps his way into end zone for 4th TD
videos.description: Rashaad Penny receives the handoff and pushes his way through for another Aztec touchdown.

videos.headline: Army's Woolfolk gets last second TD
videos.description: Darnell Woolfolk pushes his way through the defense for a Black Knights' touchdown, putting them one point away from victory and 18 seconds on the clock.

videos.headline: Army goes for two-point conversion to win game
videos.description: Army's Kell Walker runs towards the pylon for the go-ahead two-point conversion.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army goes for two-point conversion to win game) 2017/12/23

videos.headline: Army spoils SDSU's last-gasp play with insane TD
videos.description: SDSU runs a hook-and-ladder play in their its hopes to make a last-second comeback, but a lateral is picked off and returned to the end zone by Army's Elijah Riley.

videos.headline: Army is presented the Lockheed Martin Armed Forces trophy
videos.description: Jeff Monken and the captains of the Black Knights accept the Lockheed Martin Armed Forces trophy.

videos.headline: Bradshaw on the class that changed Army football
videos.description: Army senior Ahmad Bradshaw shares how his team beat San Diego State and how his class transformed the Army football program.

videos.headline: Army beats San Diego State in wild ending
videos.description: Army gets a late touchdown and scores a two-point conversion in an eventual 42-35 victory. In the loss, San Diego State's Rashaad Penny rushed for 221 yards and four touchdowns.
